- The string parameter `word` must not be null.
- The integer result is the minimum total distance to type the string parameter `word` using only two fingers.
- The total distance calculation must consider the distance between coordinates of each letter in the string parameter `word`.
- The initial positions of the two fingers are considered free and do not count towards the total distance.
- The two fingers do not have to start at the first letter or the first two letters of the string parameter `word`.